1.0.name: wordpress/prana
1.0.description: Prana is a beautiful theme with simple and clean design. Theme can easily be used as a personal portfolio, simple blog or a complete business website. There is an impressive typography by Google Web Fonts without the need for load-heavy graphics. Some exciting features of Prana are custom menu, custom background, custom flexible header, featured images, widgetized sidebar, threaded comments, improved SEO performance and theme options. Make it yours with a custom menu and  a custom flexible header for anything you like to suit your own niche.
